long_description: Enjoy a different kind of jerky on your next adventure. Five Star Ahi Tuna jerky delivers great taste and comes in a convenient resealable bag. Needs no refrigeration so it can easily be taken on long trips. No preparation necessary; eat the jerky right out of the package. Resealable bag makes keeping jerky fresh on the trail easy. Five Star Ahi Tuna jerky contains no added MSG. *Discount will be applied when you check out; offer not valid for sale-price items ending in $._3 or $._9.
